something other than valentina.

17:06.693 --> 17:09.560
Right. Sorry.
Go ahead.

17:10.497 --> 17:13.131
I mean, she's making
the biggest mistake of her life,

17:13.133 --> 17:14.165
But...Go ahead.

17:14.166 --> 17:15.333
Zoila, breathe.

17:15.335 --> 17:16.733
She's not getting married
tonight.

17:16.736 --> 17:18.703
Oh, she's not
getting married <i> ever.</i>

17:18.704 --> 17:20.405
No one is
marrying anyone.

17:22.342 --> 17:24.809
Ah. Here we go.

17:24.810 --> 17:26.778
Uh, hold on.
[ chuckles ]

17:26.780 --> 17:30.314
Zoila, i know we've only
been together a short time,

17:30.316 --> 17:33.684
But...You're the most
important person
in the world to me.

17:33.686 --> 17:35.119
[ chuckles ]

17:35.121 --> 17:37.221
Just a second.

17:37.223 --> 17:40.124
You're so funny and smart
and beautiful.

17:40.126 --> 17:41.759
And hungry.

17:41.761 --> 17:43.528
Why won't you just let me
have a moment?

17:43.530 --> 17:44.562
