i had it all planned out.

17:55.575 --> 17:57.742
You would open it,
your eyes would fill with tears,

17:57.744 --> 18:00.244
We would tell the story
to our grandchildren, but now...

18:00.246 --> 18:02.680
You were gonna propose.

18:02.682 --> 18:03.748
Yes.

18:03.750 --> 18:05.216
[ sighs ]

18:05.218 --> 18:07.518
