really, really love you.

18:09.556 --> 18:13.124
'cause i still want
to do this.

18:13.126 --> 18:16.427
Zoila,
<i>te quiero mÃ¡s que nadie.</i>

18:16.429 --> 18:18.396
Will you marry me?

18:21.167 --> 18:23.801
Oh, my god.
What am i gonna tell valentina?

18:30.643 --> 18:32.477
So,
you find me a job yet?
Nothing yet.

18:32.479 --> 18:34.445
