18:54.501 --> 18:56.801
Oh!
I start tomorrow!

18:56.803 --> 18:58.636
Oh, that is wonderful,
alma.

18:58.638 --> 19:01.572
Well,
thank you for stopping by.

19:01.574 --> 19:02.807
