something.

19:05.645 --> 19:06.844
She did, huh?

19:06.846 --> 19:08.179
It was nothing.

19:08.181 --> 19:10.414
What? You --
you're a miracle worker.

19:10.416 --> 19:13.551
If she can find <i> me</i> a job,
she can find anyone a job.

19:13.553 --> 19:15.219
Good luck.
Bye-bye. Thank you.

19:15.221 --> 19:17.421
I'm gonna call you and...
Okay.

19:17.423 --> 19:19.257
