that job.

19:23.396 --> 19:25.830
I-it wasn't really right
for you.
Why not?

19:25.832 --> 19:27.899
You have
all these requirements --

19:27.901 --> 19:30.201
A house by the beach,
no vacuuming.

19:30.203 --> 19:32.603
Forget all that.
I'll take anything.

19:32.605 --> 19:33.838
Just find me work.

19:33.840 --> 19:35.473
