19:49.455 --> 19:51.589
Eh, now and then.
It's not that bad, is it?

19:51.591 --> 19:53.257
It's a pigsty!

19:53.259 --> 19:55.426
Then it's a good thing
you're coming home, right?

19:55.428 --> 19:57.461
So i can clean it
for you?

19:57.463 --> 19:59.263
You are really good
at it.

19:59.265 --> 20:00.531
Spence!

20:00.533 --> 20:03.334
What? It's your job.
Loo-- i'm an actor.

20:03.336 --> 20:04.602
I wouldn't be offended
if you asked me

20:04.604 --> 20:06.938
To perform a monologue
or cry on cue.

20:06.940 --> 20:10.408
When we first met,
i was your maid.

20:10.410 --> 20:12.610
But now i am your <i> wife.</i>

20:16.516 --> 20:18.950
Of course you are.

20:18.952 --> 20:20.418
I'm sorry.

20:20.420 --> 20:22.520
I will hire someone
to clean it up.

20:22.522 --> 20:24.922
