20:24.924 --> 20:26.624
Me?

20:26.626 --> 20:28.659
Well,
don't act so surprised.

20:28.661 --> 20:32.530
When i was married to ernesto,
we always shared the housework.

20:32.532 --> 20:34.865
I just think a cleaning lady
will do a better job.

20:34.867 --> 20:37.969
But you got to learn
how to save money,<i> papi,</i>

20:37.971 --> 20:39.737
