gonna have any.

20:39.739 --> 20:42.340
Okay.

20:42.342 --> 20:44.575
When you get home,
the place will be spotless.

20:44.577 --> 20:46.944
And you won't hire anyone
to clean?

20:46.946 --> 20:49.580
I won't. I promise.

20:49.582 --> 20:50.815
[ chuckles ]

20:50.817 --> 20:52.750
[ sniffs ]

20:52.752 --> 20:53.818
[ exhales deeply ]

20:53.820 --> 20:55.319
What?

20:55.321 --> 20:58.689
You might want to start
with the laundry.

20:58.691 --> 21:00.858
[ doorbell rings ]

21:05.765 --> 21:07.832
May i help you?

21:07.834 --> 21:09.834
Detective figueroa.
Beverly hills police.

21:09.836 --> 21:12.036
Oh, is everything
all right?

21:12.038 --> 21:13.537
We're canvassing
the neighborhood

21:13.539 --> 21:15.273
For leads on a case.

21:15.275 --> 21:16.507
Were you at home
the night before last?

21:16.509 --> 21:17.875
I-i was.

21:17.877 --> 21:19.543
And did you see or hear
anything unusual?

21:19.545 --> 21:22.380
Not really, sorry.
What is this about?

21:22.382 --> 21:24.849
A severed leg was found at the
powell residence down the road.

21:24.851 --> 21:26.517
Oh, my god. A leg?

21:26.519 --> 21:28.352
And we think it belonged
to someone who was murdered

21:28.354 --> 21:29.654
In the area
two nights ago.

21:29.656 --> 21:32.023
[ gasps ]
that's horrible.

21:32.025 --> 21:34.725
Don't worry, ma'am.
We'll catch the killer.

21:34.727 --> 21:37.728
I'll leave you my card
in case something comes to mind.

21:37.730 --> 21:39.630
Thank you, detective.

21:46.406 --> 21:47.905
You lied to me.

21:47.907 --> 21:50.574
[ sighs ]

21:53.946 --> 21:56.047
Thanks for coming over.

21:56.049 --> 21:58.516
I hate
the way we left things.

21:58.518 --> 22:02.086
You act like getting married
is the worst thing in the world.

22:02.088 --> 22:04.722
Yeah, about that...

22:04.724 --> 22:07.458
I think i was wrong.

22:07.460 --> 22:10.561
Did you just say
you were wrong?

22:10.563 --> 22:14.332
Marriage really is
a wonderful, sacred thing.

22:14.334 --> 22:15.766
So i have your blessing?

22:15.768 --> 22:19.403
I support you 100%.

22:21.641 --> 22:24.608
In a bit
of unrelated news,

22:24.610 --> 22:27.611
Javi and i
are also getting married.

22:27.613 --> 22:29.113
What?

22:29.115 --> 22:30.915
I know.
It's a bit sudden, but --

22:30.917 --> 22:33.384
You've only been together
for less than a year.

22:33.386 --> 22:34.452
What's the rush?

22:34.454 --> 22:38.489
Well...I'm pregnant.

22:38.491 --> 22:41.692
Oh, my god.

22:41.694 --> 22:43.494
And since i've been
so supportive of you and remi --

22:43.496 --> 22:45.429
<i>Papi</i> just died.

22:45.431 --> 22:48.399
And now you're getting married?
And having a baby?

22:48.401 --> 22:50.735
I didn't plan
any of this.

22:50.737 --> 22:52.903
But, sweetheart,
i could really use your support.

22:52.905 --> 22:53.938
No.

22:53.940 --> 22:56.006
Valentina --

22:56.008 --> 22:59.110
You do not have my blessing.
And you never will.

23:03.683 --> 23:05.383
[ door opens ]

23:05.385 --> 23:06.684
[ door slams ]

23:06.686 --> 23:09.820
