i-i-i can explain.

23:09.822 --> 23:11.789
No. You told me
the burglar ran away.

23:11.791 --> 23:13.824
How did he run away
with a missing leg?

23:13.826 --> 23:14.859
Well...

23:14.861 --> 23:16.660
I'm not stupid.

23:16.662 --> 23:18.829
He's dead, isn't he?

23:18.831 --> 23:20.865
Yes.

23:20.867 --> 23:22.133
Oh, my god.

23:22.135 --> 23:25.169
What really happened?
Did you kill him?

23:25.171 --> 23:27.405
It's probably better
if you don't know.

23:27.407 --> 23:30.808
All right, uh...Listen,
maybe if it was self-defense,

23:30.810 --> 23:32.576
The cops will understand.

23:32.578 --> 23:34.612
I can't have the police
looking into our lives.

23:34.614 --> 23:35.980
Why not?
Because of katy.

23:37.650 --> 23:39.550
Her adoption
wasn't legal,

23:39.552 --> 23:41.051
And if it comes out,
we'll lose her.

23:41.053 --> 23:44.889
You know what,
this is insane.

23:44.891 --> 23:47.892
I don't want to be involved
in any of this.

23:47.894 --> 23:50.027
Look, look, look, you don't
have to work here anymore,

23:50.029 --> 23:51.495
But don't go to
the police.

23:51.497 --> 23:54.465
I am begging you.
For katy's sake.

23:54.467 --> 23:58.736
Your keys
are on the kitchen counter.

24:07.980 --> 24:09.847
Son of a bitch.

24:09.849 --> 24:10.881
[ sighs ]

24:10.883 --> 24:12.650
[ doorbell rings ]

24:14.854 --> 24:17.555
Hi.

24:17.557 --> 24:18.789
Ladies.
What are you doing here?

24:18.791 --> 24:20.558
