let me give you the tour.

24:39.612 --> 24:40.644
Oh, we'd love to.

24:40.646 --> 24:42.079
I-i have to apologize.

24:42.081 --> 24:44.715
The place is, uh, eh,
it's a little bit of a mess.

24:44.717 --> 24:46.951
[ chuckles ]
it's not so bad.

24:46.953 --> 24:48.252
