your tetanus shot.

24:48.254 --> 24:49.587
Mm-hmm.

24:49.589 --> 24:52.223
I've just been
really busy...

24:52.225 --> 24:53.724
Taking care of miguel.

24:53.726 --> 24:57.862
He's not buried
in here somewhere, is he?

24:57.864 --> 25:00.998
No, no. He's in his room
playing video games.

25:01.000 --> 25:04.001
Helps him
keep his mind off of...

25:04.003 --> 25:06.270
How hard
things have been...

25:06.272 --> 25:09.039
