rosie's gone.

25:09.041 --> 25:11.175
Oh, oh! Ooh, ooh, ooh!
It's okay.

25:11.177 --> 25:12.710
It's okay, it's okay.

25:12.712 --> 25:14.512
I'm sorry.
[ chuckles ]

25:14.514 --> 25:16.814
I'm supposed to be
the one keeping it together.

25:16.816 --> 25:19.016
It's all right.
Let it out.

25:19.018 --> 25:22.987
Ah, there is
