25:43.943 --> 25:45.042
[ sighs ]

25:45.044 --> 25:46.277
All right.

25:46.279 --> 25:48.812
Fine. We'll help.

25:48.814 --> 25:50.047
No, no.

25:50.049 --> 25:51.282
