26:02.662 --> 26:03.994
[ sighs ]

26:10.770 --> 26:12.202
Can you believe it?

26:12.204 --> 26:13.704
After the way
she raised me,

26:13.706 --> 26:15.573
And now she's
the one who's knocked up?

26:15.575 --> 26:17.207
Maybe you should just
be happy for her.

26:17.209 --> 26:18.909
